## Not Just Task Management

Remember: this skill is for **cross-source coherence**, not task management. Use it to answer questions like:

- "Did I create tasks for the intentions I wrote about last week?"
- "Which tasks have been open longest?"
- "Am I completing tasks in line with the goals in my notes?"

Use your actual task manager for actually managing tasks.
